title: Nutanix Prism: General info about a cluster
agents: special
catalog: os/storage
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check returns general information about the cluster, in particular its name and
 firmware version.

 This check requires the special agent configurable through "Nutanix Prism".

inventory:
 Exactly one item will be discovered if the configured server can be reached.
